s ridged with a fin which is often mistaken for a mermaid's."},{"version":"blue","text":"Lives close to water. Its long tail is ridged with a fin which is often mistaken for a mermaid's."},{"version":"yellow","text":"Its cell structure is similar to water molecules. It will melt away and become invis\u00ad ible in water."},{"version":"gold","text":"When VAPOREON's fins begin to vi\u00ad brate, it is a sign that rain will come within a few hours."},{"version":"silver","text":"It prefers beauti\u00ad ful shores. With cells similar to water molecules, it could melt in water."},{"version":"crystal","text":"As it uses the fins on the tip of its tail to swim, it blends with the water perfectly."},{"version":"ruby","text":"VAPOREON underwent a spontaneous mutation and grew fins and gills that allow it to live underwater. This POK\u00e9MON has the ability to freely control water."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"VAPOREON underwent a spontaneous mutation and grew fins and gills that allow it to live underwater. This POK\u00e9MON has the ability to freely control water."},{"version":"emerald","text":"VAPOREON underwent a spontaneous mutation and grew fins and gills that allow them to live underwater. They have the ability to freely control water."},{"version":"firered","text":"Its body\u2019s cellular structure is similar to the molecular composition of water. It can melt invisibly in water."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Lives close to water. Its long tail is ridged with a fin which is often mistaken for a mermaid\u2019s."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It has evolved to be suitable for an aquatic life. It can invisibly melt away into water."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It has evolved to be suitable for an aquatic life. It can invisibly melt away into water."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Its cell composition is similar to water molecules. As a result, it can melt away into water."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"When VAPOREON\u2019s fins begin to vibrate, it is a sign that rain will come within a few hours."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It prefers beautiful shores. With cells similar to water molecules, it could melt in water."},{"version":"black","text":"Its cell composition is similar to water molecules. As a result, it can melt away into water."},{"version":"white","text":"Its cell composition is similar to water molecules. As a result, it can melt away into water."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Its cell composition is similar to water molecules. As a result, it can\u2019t be seen when it melts away into water."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Its cell composition is similar to water molecules. As a result, it can\u2019t be seen when it melts away into water."},{"version":"x","text":"It prefers beautiful shores. With cells similar to water molecules, it could melt in water."},{"version":"y","text":"It has evolved to be suitable for an aquatic life. It can invisibly melt away into water."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Vaporeon underwent a spontaneous mutation and grew fins and gills that allow it to live underwater. This Pok\u00e9mon has the ability to freely control water."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Vaporeon underwent a spontaneous mutation and grew fins and gills that allow it to live underwater. This Pok\u00e9mon has the ability to freely control water."},{"version":"sun","text":"Its cells are composed of units much like water molecules. It lives close to water and is often mistaken for a mermaid."},{"version":"moon","text":"Blending in with the water and erasing all signs of its presence, it patiently waits for its prey, fish Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Clean, clear waters are its usual habitat. When it\u2019s about to be attacked by an invading enemy, it dives into the water to hide."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It detects nearby moisture with its fin. When its fin begins trembling rapidly, that means rain will fall in a few hours."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Its cell structur